                 </svg> <span title="Всего голосов 17: ↑16 и ↓1" class="tm-votes-meter__value tm-votes-meter__value_positive tm-votes-meter__value_appearance-article tm-votes-meter__value_rating">+15</span>
                </div> <span title="Количество просмотров" class="tm-icon-counter tm-data-icons__item">
